 data-config=\"{&quot;rtl&quot;:false,&quot;arrows&quot;:true,&quot;dots&quot;:false,&quot;initial_slide&quot;:null,&quot;pauseOnHover&quot;:true,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;speed&quot;:1000,&quot;slidesPerGroup&quot;:1,&quot;slidesPerView&quot;:3,&quot;loop&quot;:true,&quot;breakpoints&quot;:{&quot;320&quot;:{&quot;slidesPerView&quot;:1,&quot;slidesPerGroup&quot;:1,&quot;spaceBetween&quot;:10},&quot;768&quot;:{&quot;slidesPerView&quot;:1,&quot;slidesPerGroup&quot;:1,&quot;spaceBetween&quot;:10},&quot;1024&quot;:{&quot;slidesPerView&quot;:3,&quot;slidesPerGroup&quot;:1,&quot;spaceBetween&quot;:24}}}\">\r\n            <!-- Slider main container -->\r\n            <div class=\"rkit-swiper\">\r\n                                <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n                    <!-- Slides -->\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1-819x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1260\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1-768x960.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-11-1.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Experi\u00eancia Ecol\u00f3gica                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Localizado em uma reserva ambiental, o Uni celebra a natureza como protagonista. Trilhas ecol\u00f3gicas, observa\u00e7\u00e3o de p\u00e1ssaros, jardinagem regenerativa e programas de conscientiza\u00e7\u00e3o ambiental convidam os h\u00f3spedes a uma imers\u00e3o respons\u00e1vel. Cada a\u00e7\u00e3o busca preservar o ecossistema local, transformando a estadia em uma experi\u00eancia de conex\u00e3o e respeito.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Copia-de-Pratos-Uni-1.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1237\" alt=\"\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                La Dolce Vita                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">A arte de viver bem se manifesta em cada detalhe no Uni. Momentos lentos de degusta\u00e7\u00e3o, p\u00f4res do sol na varanda, leituras contemplativas, vinhos selecionados e experi\u00eancias gastron\u00f4micas que celebram o prazer simples. Inspirado na cultura italiana, o hotel convida a saborear a vida sem pressa, valorizando a qualidade dos momentos.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1452\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14-768x960.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-UNI-reeditadas-14-1229x1536.jpg 1229w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Piscina climatizada                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">A piscina do Uni parece flutuar sobre o mar.\nO cen\u00e1rio se abre em tons de azul, com a Praia Brava ao fundo e o sol refletindo sobre a \u00e1gua. Um convite para mergulhar na calma e na beleza \u2014 como nos terra\u00e7os da Costa Amalfitana.\n<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1087\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-canon-15-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Bar da Piscina                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Desfrute de drinks especialmente preparados para voc\u00ea saborear enquanto admira a Praia da Ferradura e seu p\u00f4r-do-sol inesquec\u00edvel de uma perspectiva \u00fanica.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1836\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-10-e1760532182805.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1117\" a