sync\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1454\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_.webp 1600w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_-200x300.webp 200w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_-683x1024.webp 683w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_-768x1152.webp 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_-1024x1536.webp 1024w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-16-_1_-1365x2048.webp 1365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                SPA                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Inspirado nos rituais mediterr\u00e2neos de bem-estar, o Spa do Uni \u00e9 um ref\u00fagio para o corpo e a mente.\nMassagens, terapias e aromas que convidam ao relaxamento, com o mar como pano de fundo.\n<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"883\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Copia-de-Pratos-Uni-5-e1760534728774.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1424\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Copia-de-Pratos-Uni-5-e1760534728774.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Copia-de-Pratos-Uni-5-e1760534728774-300x265.jpg 300w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Copia-de-Pratos-Uni-5-e1760534728774-768x678.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Gastronomia                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">A gastronomia do Uni combina ingredientes frescos, receitas inspiradas na costa italiana e uma carta de vinhos e drinks que celebra o prazer \u00e0 mesa.\nCada refei\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 acompanhada da vista da Praia da Ferradura \u2014 o cen\u00e1rio perfeito para brindar a vida.\n<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1964\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1455\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867.webp 1920w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867-293x300.webp 293w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867-1001x1024.webp 1001w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867-768x786.webp 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-Uni-32-_2_-e1760534968867-1502x1536.webp 1502w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Decora\u00e7\u00e3o Rom\u00e2ntica                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Poucos lugares s\u00e3o t\u00e3o inspiradores quanto o canto da Ferradura ao p\u00f4r do sol.\nO brilho do mar, o sil\u00eancio da natureza e o clima mediterr\u00e2neo criam o cen\u00e1rio perfeito para viver o amor.\n<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1456\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524.webp 1920w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524-240x300.webp 240w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524-819x1024.webp 819w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524-768x960.webp 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524-1229x1536.webp 1229w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08524-1638x2048.webp 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                \u00c1rea Kids                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Os pequenos tamb\u00e9m t\u00eam seu espa\u00e7o para brincar e imaginar.\nNa \u00e1rea kids do Uni, o lazer \u00e9 seguro, colorido e pensado para transformar as f\u00e9rias em lembran\u00e7as felizes.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1384\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_.webp 1920w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_-240x300.webp 240w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_-819x1024.webp 819w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_-768x960.webp 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_-1229x1536.webp 1229w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Copia-de-CR_08594-_1_-1638x2048.webp 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Sal\u00e3o de Jogos                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Com jogos de tabuleiro e uma mesa de sinuca, o sal\u00e3o de jogos do Uni \u00e9 um espa\u00e7o para relaxar, se divertir e viver momentos leves em boa companhia.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1574\" height=\"1775\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1076\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834.jpg 1574w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834-266x300.jpg 266w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834-908x1024.jpg 908w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834-768x866.jpg 768w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/PET-scaled-e1758809251834-1362x1536.jpg 1362w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1574px) 100vw, 1574px\" \/>                                <\/div>\r\n                                <div class=\"card-body\">\r\n                                    <div class=\"card-heading\">\r\n                                                                                <h4 class=\"card-title\">\r\n                                            <a href=\"#\">\r\n                                                Pet Friendly                                            <\/a>\r\n                                        <\/h4>\r\n                                                                                    <span class=\"card-subheading\"><\/span>\r\n                                                                            <\/div>\r\n                                    <p class=\"card-description\">Cercado por natureza e com o clima acolhedor da Praia da Ferradura, o hotel oferece o cen\u00e1rio ideal para momentos leves: caminhadas entre o verde, descanso ao sol e dias que seguem o ritmo do Mediterr\u00e2neo \u2014 livres, tranquilos e cheios de afeto.<\/p>\r\n                                                                    <\/div>\r\n                            <\/div>\r\n                        <\/div>\r\n                                            <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                            <div class=\"rkit-card default\">\r\n                                <div class=\"card-image\">\r\n                                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-62.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1166\" alt=\"Praia Ferradura\" srcset=\"https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-62.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Copia-de-Uni-62-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/uniboutiquehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploa